Tools for Managing Test Anxiety

Thursday, February 19th from 12PM - 1PM, 240 Bechtel Hall

Dear Students,
 
Join the Center for Access to Engineering Excellence and the Tang Center as we discuss tools for managing text anxiety. Many students are hindered by test anxiety, no matter much they prepare for exams. Come learn techniques for dealing with test anxiety so that you can crush your next exam! Lunch will be served, so please RSVP here:
https://docs.google.com/a/berkeley.edu/forms/d/1IG3ODIsPBGxT1plQO7u5sdzpWQi7hS74jcNT1Y3HpAU/viewform
